The paper deals with distributed storage systems, which are typically studied in the areas of information theory (cs.IT), distributed computing (cs.DC), and distributed systems (cs.DS). The use of graph theory to construct the DSS suggests that the paper may also be relevant to the subfield of network analysis (cs.NA). Finally, the focus on optimality suggests that the paper may also be relevant to the subfield of optimization (cs.SI).
